<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV94">
<l>maippaṭi mēṉiyuñ centā maraikkaṇṇum vaitikarē</l>
<l>meyppaṭi yāluṉ tiruvaṭic cūṭun takaimaiyiṉā</l>
<l>reppaṭi yūrā milaikkak kuruṭṭā milaikkumeṉṉu</l>
<l>mappaṭi yāṉuñcoṉ ṉēṉaṭi yēṉmaṟṟi yāteṉpaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Veda-adherents only, by [their] manner of truth, are fit to wear the holy feet</l>
<l>of you with kajal body and red lotus eyes [on their heads].</l>
<l>“The way the blind cow will graze when the cows from any village will graze”,</l>
<l>I too spoke in that manner. What else can I say who am [your] servant?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
